Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Women's Lib, 1975
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8qk5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Mar 1975
Equal Rights amendment to the US constitution causes splits in both women's and men's liberation groups. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less